- Use the App Router for better performance and organization of routes.
- Implement proper error boundaries to handle errors gracefully.
- Utilize built-in data fetching methods (getStaticProps, getServerSideProps) for optimal data management.
- Optimize images using the Next.js Image component for faster load times.

